    From the manufacturer

    Stylish & Durable Spacious Laptop Backpack

    Ideal for everyday use; the AmazonBasics Laptop Bag is designed to carry your laptop, charging accessories and stationary. Two two zippered compartments come handy in efficient organizing of your backpack contents.

    Water Repellent & Wear Resistant

    The premium quality polyester used to make this bag, repells water without absorbing it to keep your laptop safe. The sturdy material is wear resistant which makes the bag durable and longer lasting.

    Adjustable Shoulder Straps

    The adjustable shoulder straps ensure a snug fit which distributes weight evenly across your shoulders, making it easy to carry the bag wherever you go

    Multipurpose

    The laptop bagpack is perfect for daily use. The convenience of two zippered compartments allows you to comfortably store mobile phones, chargers and other smaller items. You can also use it as an overnight bag for a weekend getaway

    Good Looking & Comfortable

    The intelligent and ergonomic design of this laptop back is convenient, comfortable and stylish
